&lt;li&gt;Draft, review, and negotiate contracts across all business areas, ensuring alignment with company objectives and compliance with applicable laws.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support contract drafting and review for Wave&#39;s core products and services, ensuring the protection of the company&#39;s commercial and legal interests while optimizing value and efficiency.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead and participate in complex, high-value contract negotiations, providing strategic legal input to achieve balanced, sustainable agreements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Enhance and manage the contracting process, including the implementation of contract policies, contract management systems, electronic signature tools, and document archiving procedures.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Legal Operations&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Implement group legal policies and propose updates based on legal developments, operational feedback, and industry best practices (e.g., contract policy, data privacy policy).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
