&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and apply procedures for managing legal claims and disputes, including pre-litigation strategy, mediation, arbitration, and litigation follow-up.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;People Support&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
